<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Notification: Response to Your Question</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>You've Got a Response!</h2>
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>We are excited to let you know that there has been a response to your question "<strong><%= question %></strong>"</p>
        <p><strong>Course name:</strong> <%= courseName %></p>
        <p>Login to your course to view the response and continue the discussion</p>
        <p>If you have any further questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out. Happy learning!</p>
        <p>Best regards,E-learning</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
